.I val substring 
: 
.B string -> int -> int -> t
.sp

.B Digest\&.substring s ofs len
returns the digest of the substring
of 
.B s
starting at index 
.B ofs
and containing 
.B len
characters\&.

.sp

.I val subbytes 
: 
.B bytes -> int -> int -> t
.sp

.B Digest\&.subbytes s ofs len
returns the digest of the subsequence
of 
.B s
starting at index 
.B ofs
and containing 
.B len
bytes\&.

.sp
.B "Since"
4.02.0

.sp

.I val channel 
: 
.B Pervasives.in_channel -> int -> t
.sp
If 
.B len
is nonnegative, 
.B Digest\&.channel ic len
reads 
.B len
characters from channel 
.B ic
and returns their digest, or raises
.B End_of_file
if end\-of\-file is reached before 
.B len
characters
are read\&.  If 
.B len
is negative, 
.B Digest\&.channel ic len
reads
all characters from 
.B ic
until end\-of\-file is reached and return
their digest\&.

.sp

